OL,5,G2240 Designing the Hebrides
OL,6,     FNew. Bothy: The team update a
OL,7,     Fcrumbling bothy on the small
OL,8,     Fisland of Ulva, which locals want
OL,9,     Fto rent out to visitors. With no
OL,10,     Fpower, water or easy access, Banjo
OL,11,     Fhas his work cut out.
OL,12,G2320 Nurses on the Ward
OL,13,     FCaroline treats an unvaccinated
OL,14,     FCovid patient who's been in a coma
OL,15,     Ffor weeks. Matron Hazera assesses
OL,16,     Fa deep tissue injury and Kat cares
OL,17,     Ffor a man in pain after kidney
OL,18,     Fstone surgery.
